				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ \mathcal{B} ({\mu \rightarrow \hbox {e} \gamma })$$\end{document} is predicted at an observable level 10-11\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
