				\begin{document}$$\approx 350$$\end{document} ps.

The method was tested during a beam test with a pTC prototype at PSI. The time resolution was measured by comparing the measured times of two adjacent pixels, where the transit time spread of the positron along that path is ≈50\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
