The resolutions on the relevant physical variables are expected to improve by about a factor of 2, as suggested by simulation and preliminary results from laboratory and beam tests. Those improvements, together with an increase by more than a factor of 2 both in muon decay rate and signal detection efficiency, are expected to bring the sensitivity to the μ+→e+γ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
